## 7. Layer 4 — Sensor Specification Requirements

### Minimum Sensor Set — Physical Layer
```
- FMCW LiDAR         (R measurement and radius-jump detection)
- Standard LiDAR     (θ computation via point cloud normals)
  or depth camera
- IMU + wheel odometry  (V dynamic computation)
```

### Minimum Sensor Set — Semantic Layer
```
- RGB camera         (scene semantic recognition)
- HD map access      (traffic rule localization)
- Network interface  (LLM semantic API — local deployment optional)
```

