## 10. One-sentence Value Statement

> Use the certainty of physics to hold the safety boundary.  
> Use the flexibility of semantics to handle rule complexity.  
> Between them: only one multiplication.

---

## 11. Implementation Pathways

This specification serves as the shared top-level reference for three implementation approaches developed in this repository:

**Bypass Implementation** — Add TMF as a parallel audit layer alongside existing systems. Lowest engineering risk. Recommended first step.

**Insertion Implementation** — Integrate TMF layers into an existing pipeline at defined interface points.

**Greenfield Implementation** — Build a TMF-native navigation stack from scratch. Most complete. Highest effort.

